Detailed Description

Base interface for suppliers providing synchrone processing of single object with "pull data" model.

Additional interfaces (providers) should provide access to intern stored produced objects. For example image provider should provide method {const i2d::CRectangle* GetAoi() const}. The internal stored object should be created on demand.

Definition at line 58 of file ISupplier.h.

enum iproc::ISupplier::WorkStatus
Enumerator:
WS_INVALID 

Supplier is invalidated and will produce new result on demand.

WS_INIT 

New work is initialized.

WS_LOCKED 

Supplier is locked becouse it is doing processing step.

WS_OK 

Work was done correctly and no error occure.

WS_CANCELED 

Work was canceled.

WS_ERROR 

Work was done, but there were errors.

WS_CRITICAL 

Work cannot be done.
